=====
spinn
=====

spinn is a sample application to show how to use a fake device manager to test
your code.


Compile and run
---------------

    mkdir build
    cd build

    cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -D BUILD_TESTING=YES ..

    make

    ./spinn

    cd ..

To run the tests
----------------
Requires stmm-input-fake to be installed

    cd test

    make test
